data.value:
To better understand the issue, please help share the following details while reporting bugs in EliteWork tracker application.
1. Brief description - what happens, what you think etc. 2. Steps to reproduce - how can we reproduce the bug? 3. Actual result - what result you are getting? 4. Expected result - what result you are expecting? 5. Priority (Low/High/Medium) - expected time to fix?
Thank you for your patience.
